org.apache.jena.jdbc.results.metadata

Class JenaResultsMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.jdbc.results.metadata.AbstractResultsMetadata
      • org.apache.jena.jdbc.results.metadata.JenaResultsMetadata
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSetMetaData, Wrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AskResultsMetadata, SelectResultsMetadata, TripleResultsMetadata

    public abstract class JenaResultsMetadata
extends AbstractResultsMetadata
    Abstract implementation of result set metadata for Jena JDBC result sets, specially for JenaResultSet implementations.

    This differs from the base AbstractResultsMetadata in that it provides a strongly typed method for accessing the JenaResultSet which may be useful for some advanced metadata implementations.
